{"tid":2282122,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[大眾共識]論鬼㓕入面最失敗既角色","createTime":"2020-11-11T15:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T08:58:55.000Z","uid":117275,"like":13,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"daeaaebe48a7c7a11ef32992972fbb783802046a","tid":2282122,"uid":117275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:15:32.000Z","msg":"1.無慘 沒有之一<br />\n<br />\n性格on9: <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成個角色好矛盾 自己吹到幾勁幾勁 但其實驚日呼劍士驚到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地連小小耳飾都要趕盡殺絕 試想下 如果一開波 <br />\n<br />\n唔係因為個 耳飾 , 佢全家都可能無人追殺 , 咁日呼 火神樂 又後繼無人 , 無慘基本上可以做地球之主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人設on9: <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢套野hard sell 緊 親情，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算係鬼 最尾關頭 就死都可以有走馬燈 黎 <br />\n<br />\n講其實鬼 都未必係壞 , 但無慘呢條友 除左描述佢幾衰 幾無人性 既生物外 就無再講過， 咩起始 點解成為第一隻鬼 點解要食人 , 個feel 好似純做大boss 存在 , 完全唔實在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次講住咁多先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84932c2ee80e19b77da2f3cbda7c8155f5c84867","tid":2282122,"uid":299548,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"又捉到個反鬼滅撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aphaSRr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaphaSRr.png&h=dcf33f45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5fc50273a82f0be02d39abf7fa04a1d2be201a5","tid":2282122,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"對耳飾 大陸人都好驚"},{"pid":"62e95fc54388850dbdceb4b4d2340b87cd15e770","tid":2282122,"uid":257771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84932c2ee80e